=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_Impulse_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 100 Hz, featuring instant attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with highpass character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: instant
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: highpass
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 100.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: 2.0224
  harmonic_regularity: 0.8933
  pitch_clarity: 2.5096
  inharmonicity: 0.8288
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: 6.1412
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Impulse Example 2
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/Impulse.html
// Tags: Impulse, Classes, oscillator
// ---
// --- Example 2 ---
{ Impulse.ar(800, 0.0, 0.5, 0) }.play

{ Impulse.ar(XLine.kr(800, 100, 5), 0.0, 0.5, 0) }.play
